Package sg4e.ygofm.gamedata

Record Class Card

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
sg4e.ygofm.gamedata.Card
public record Card(int id, String name, int starchips, int level, int attack, int defense, GuardianStar firstGuardianStar, GuardianStar secondGuardianStar, String description, String type, String attribute, String password, int abcSort, int maxSort, int atkSort, int defSort, int typeSort, int aiSort, int jpAbcSort, int jpMaxSort, int jpAtkSort, int jpDefSort, int jpTypeSort) extends Record
A representation of a card in Forbidden Memories. Do not instantiate this class; use FMDB to obtain card objects.
